docs.text: Bead Fourier Documentation For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. Math test \[ \int_{0}^{1} x^2 dx \] \[ \frac{ \partial p_{j}}{ \partial t} = -\frac{ \partial H}{ \partial x_{j}} \] \[ \frac{ \partial x_{j}}{ \partial t} = \frac{ \partial H}{ \partial p_{j}} = \frac{p_{j}}{m} \] \[ \frac{ \partial p_{jk}}{ \partial t} = -\frac{ \partial H}{ \partial a_{jk}}, \] \[ \frac{ \partial a_{jk}}{ \partial t} = \frac{ \partial H}{ \partial p_{jk}} = \frac{p_{jk}}{m_{k}} \]
